name: Stella McCartney Falabella Cham Flap Wallet
description:
Brand new Stella McCartney wallet from her 2013 collection: it is simply too pretty and too shiny to ignore. It is also sturdy and have the classic Flabella chain design.

Wallet comes in pretty original box.

I bought this wallet on a trip at a TJMaxx Runway store, at a $399+tax from its $560 original price. All TJMaxx around me are not Runway and do not accept high end designer return. Please let me know if you want more pictures or have other question.

This is exactly the same wallet at a much higher premium from Stella website (but different color)

http://www.stellamccartney.com/us/stella-mccartney/wallets_cod46279966ab.html

The color is similar to this item on Farfetch (but their wallet is not of current season)

http://www.farfetch.com/shopping/women/stella-mccartney-falabella-zip-wallet-item-10310644.aspx
